nodes.text: A Wookiee individual was enslaved by the Zabrak slaver Zarien Kheev, who was allied with the Galactic Empire during the early Galactic Civil War. The Wookiee was being kept in Kheev's slave camp in Mos Eisley. In 0 BBY, the Rebel agent Rianna Saren infiltrated the camp, searching for Kheev. The Wookiee advised her to deactivate the main security generator, which would allow her to reach Kheev in his main tower. In gratitude, Saren released the Wookiee and the other slaves.
